data.description: Ranch style home on an acre lot in Haslet and Northwest Schools. Immaculate inside with open concept and split floorplan. Beautiful kitchen with tons of cabinets, island, granite counters open to living space with wood burning fireplace featuring stone from bottom to top. Crown Molding, spacious bedrooms, office, formal dining or living, and oversized garage. Fourth bedroom is currently being used as game room and has private access to the backyard. Golf lovers will enjoy leisure in the backyard as you tee off for a hole in one on the par 1 while others enjoy a drink on one of many of the sitting areas. A must see!
